---
title: Honey Mustard Sausages with Sweet Potato Mash and Sticky Red Onion Gravy
description: Teaching people new skills is something which makes us pretty happy and this red onion gravy is no exception. Once you've mastered it (which should take about 4 minutes), you'll never go back to the bought stuff again! Our top tip is to use the water the potatoes are boiled in - it helps make great thick gravy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-mustard-sausages-dbe45601-e260360d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/honey-mustard-sausages-5ee2116ecf4c295f1a678a42-fc961747.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 35m
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/honey-mustard-sausages-5ee2116ecf4c295f1a678a42
author: Mimi Morley
